{"tid":1627823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫推]  神獸同裝修個對象 應該點選擇？","createTime":"2019-10-05T18:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T22:16:34.000Z","uid":30910,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5350dbc1d2137e411da47fc35e263bf4e57178ec","tid":1627823,"uid":30910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:07:34.000Z","msg":"近排成日有人話 唔好去邊到裝修<br />\n唔好亂咁用神獸<br />\n唔好呀 民意 乜乜柒柒 <br />\n<br />\n其實邊啲應該用 邊啲唔應該用 <br />\n其實好簡單<br />\n<br />\n如果一間鋪頭 你聽到佢啲員工<span style=\"color: green;\">講</span>啲言論<br />\n抵死呀 乜乜柒柒<br />\n咁依啲就唔洗裝修<br />\n開佢名同大家講<br />\n等大家唔好再去<br />\n唔比錢佢賺<br />\n<br />\n如果間鋪頭 佢扮好放<span style=\"color: red;\">陷阱</span>放手足入鋪<br />\n之後報狗 拉啲手足<br />\n咁就可以裝修<br />\n<br />\n分別係邊呢？<br />\n就係一個只係<span style=\"color: green;\">言語</span>上<br />\n一個有做出<span style=\"color: red;\">實質傷害</span><br />\n<br />\n神獸都係 如果佢埋黎<span style=\"color: green;\">開口</span>屌你<br />\n曱甴 暴徒 食屎 屌你老味<br />\n你可以屌番佢 <br />\n但唔可以用神獸<br />\n<br />\n但如果佢唔夠你屌 <br />\n開始<span style=\"color: red;\">出手</span>啦 推你 打你一巴 鐘你一拳<br />\n咁你就可以用神獸<br />\n因為佢有做到實質嘅傷害<br />\n<br />\n咁美心點解又可以裝修？<br />\n佢都係個老細講下野？<br />\n因為佢係<span style=\"color: red;\">公開</span>咁作出不實嘅指控<br />\n意圖<span style=\"color: red;\">誣蔑</span>手足<br />\n所以可以裝修<br />\n<br />\n但如果佢只係<span style=\"color: green;\">私底下</span>講呢？<br />\n咁就只可以開美心名<br />\n大家唔食 唔比錢佢賺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁中銀果啲<span style=\"color: red;\">國企</span>又點解可以裝修<br />\n因為佢地就係中共<br />\n而中共已經有好明確嘅目標<br />\n就係要係各行各業清洗我地香港人<br />\n所以就可以裝修<br />\n<br />\n基本上只要係隸屬<span style=\"color: red;\">國企</span><br />\n基本上都唔會有錯<br />\n因為從來都係中共係背後落order<br />\n從來都係敵人 而且依班人永遠唔可以同我地企埋同一邊<br />\n佢地目的永遠都唔係賺錢為第一位<br />\n而係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗</span></span>我地<br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位手足唔好比怒氣遮蓋我地雙眼<br />\n依兩樣野用得好 好有幫助<br />\n用唔好 傷害都好大<br />\n<br />\n認同唔該幫推<br />\n認同唔該幫推<br />\n認同唔該幫推<br />\n認同唔該幫推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五點訴求 缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span>"},{"pid":"988738d3cf724804d50bf3a29aba559af24704b0","tid":1627823,"uid":30910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:09:25.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1aaa121a9efd840b2c33b1a1bdbdc262270510a5","tid":1627823,"uid":30910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:09:52.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"25625f409d51a545ea702d69fd53d46f069e0e44","tid":1627823,"uid":30910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"fc2a6da3c3379fa846049c91fd82ce4345de3fbb","tid":1627823,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:13:03.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"4d5c2be7f5c0750dcb5c5de29f8753faabf4b69e","tid":1627823,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:13:13.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"f50c2b27c734c4dd2c7ce4688237991497a53ca7","tid":1627823,"uid":330823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:13:22.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"94189e44afe1c6f97ed70a2835e697b09e17d534","tid":1627823,"uid":30910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:15:29.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"f41ad5343a1f60c8439a4bfe2310d3a4705b2c57","tid":1627823,"uid":30910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:16:34.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"69d4c112a00c47d74cb18b08639f86985beee41e","tid":1627823,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:19:40.000Z","msg":"人地話美心唔裝修<br />\n不過唔割"},{"pid":"54bde3b508871da67aab09f454cde9bd570d1cf1","tid":1627823,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"推啊！！"},{"pid":"ad909699d37c07eb0175f84e5c365155c9ad927b","tid":1627823,"uid":70115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"fd9a0f56cd58354b0ac3204b07c675ae3548f64b","tid":1627823,"uid":138051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,